i/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來有新款"},{"pid":"9a07a401b399b9787f2267ca5bf747012654559e","tid":710950,"uid":103207,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.cafedecoralfastfood.com/files/image/hk/%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E4%B8%89%E6%96%87%E6%B2%BB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cafedecoralfastfood.com%2Ffiles%2Fimage%2Fhk%2F%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E4%25B8%2589%25E6%2596%2587%25E6%25B2%25BB.jpg&h=83a47257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前食過大家樂公司三文治(有幾塊薯片)覺得垃圾既,<br />\n<br />\n真係要食一次,轉左真係唔同晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df7d32d7d336f9c6cd77e8205dce4b9f96c5f5b","tid":710950,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9eff16d1725e8c93767dd6ba8938d865a2b9d674","tid":710950,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:09:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我返港島,大家樂d食物水準真係好食過美心bo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪地區問題?<br />\n<br />\n間美心真係好難食</blockquote>大快活難食就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美心一般般<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你食下大家樂個早餐嘅沙嗲牛肉麵先啦<br />\n佢個面頹到就咁攞水浸<br />\n都可以話大家樂好食嘅我冇嘢好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n證明好多香港人都係唔識食野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"我唔食沙嗲牛肉麵,<br />\n<br />\n我多數食通粉,米粉,麥皮,<br />\n<br />\n沙嗲牛肉麵好少地方煮得好食,你話大家樂公仔麵垃圾,我都同意"},{"pid":"13a1bd316200dee6fbeed83b89b658253b3dede0","tid":710950,"uid":150079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T09:13:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我返港島,大家樂d食物水準真係好食過美心bo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪地區問題?<br />\n<br />\n間美心真係好難食</blockquote>大快活難食就真<i